race.description: Bet365 New Racing App Mdn Plate
race.comment: ZEACTION (6) went forward last start over 1600m at Seymour and held on well for third, beaten 1.75 lengths. Should park just off the speed despite a difficult draw. Has the class to figure prominently. REEL CRYSTAL (10) finished fourth at her last appearance over 1600m at Bairnsdale on October 12 after she was well back on straightening. Finds a suitable assignment this time and is a great chance to break through. VIVID REASONING (5) finished 3.5 lengths away in fifth last time out over 1600m at Bairnsdale two weeks ago. Tackles a longer journey this time. Meets a tougher line-up this time but can measure up. STRAAND DEAL (4) produced a fair effort on debut last time out when 5.5 lengths from the winner in fifth at Geelong over 1547m. Looks well placed here and has to be respected.
